DROP EXTERNAL TABLE DIM_AccessType;

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE DIM_AccessType (
	[USERTYPE] nvarchar(4000),
	[ACCESSTYPE] nvarchar(4000)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Dimensions/DIM_TYPE.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.DIM_AccessType
GO
